story.title: #EURO2016
story.description: During the #EURO2016 football competition, we are posting pairs of British Museum objects to represent the countries playing in every match. Now that the competition has reached the final 16 stage, here's a round up of the matches so far!

author.name: British Museum
author.bio: A museum of the world, for the world.
